    1. client/src/pages/coin-flip.tsx:
    TypeScript
    import { useState } from "react";
    import { Card } from "@/components/ui/card";
    import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
    import { Select, SelectContent, SelectItem, SelectTrigger, SelectValue } from "@/components/ui/select";
    import { muscleGroups } from "@shared/schema";
    import { motion, AnimatePresence } from "framer-motion";
     
    export default function CoinFlip() {
      const [selection1, setSelection1] = useState<string>();
      const [selection2, setSelection2] = useState<string>();
      const [isFlipping, setIsFlipping] = useState(false);
      const [result, setResult] = useState<string | null>(null);
     
      const handleFlip = () => {
        if (!selection1 || !selection2) return;
        
        setIsFlipping(true);
        setResult(null);
        
        // Simulate coin flip animation duration
        setTimeout(() => {
          const winner = Math.random() < 0.5 ? selection1 : selection2;
          setResult(winner);
          setIsFlipping(false);
        }, 2000);
      };
     
      return (
        <div className="min-h-screen bg-background py-8">
          <div className="container max-w-2xl">
            <Card className="p-6">
              <div className="text-center mb-6">
                <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Workout Decider</h1>
                <p className="text-muted-foreground">
                  So you can't decide what to hit today? No worries. Leave it to fate :)
                </p>
              </div>
              <AnimatePresence>
                {result && (
                  <motion.div
                    initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.5 }}
                    animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }}
                    exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.5 }}
                    className="text-center"
                  >
                    <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Today's Workout:</h2>
                    <p className="text-4xl font-black bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary/60 text-transparent bg-clip-text">
                      {result}
                    </p>
                  </motion.div>
                )}
              </AnimatePresence>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>
      );
    }
    1. client/src/pages/workout-form.tsx:
    TypeScript
    import { useForm } from "react-hook-form";
    import { zodResolver } from "@hookform/resolvers/zod";
    import { insertWorkoutSchema, muscleGroups } from "@shared/schema";
    import { Form } from "@/components/ui/form";
    import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
    import { Card } from "@/components/ui/card";
    import { Calendar } from "@/components/ui/calendar";
    import { Checkbox } from "@/components/ui/checkbox";
    import { Textarea } from "@/components/ui/textarea";
    import { useToast } from "@/hooks/use-toast";
    import { useMutation, useQueryClient } from "@tanstack/react-query";
    import { apiRequest } from "@/lib/queryClient";
    import { useLocation } from "wouter";
    import type { InsertWorkout } from "@shared/schema";
     
    function formatDateToLocalISOString(date: Date): string {
      const d = new Date(date);
      d.setMinutes(d.getMinutes() - d.getTimezoneOffset());
      return d.toISOString().split('T')[0];
    }
     
    function parseLocalDate(dateString: string): Date {
      const [year, month, day] = dateString.split('-').map(Number);
      const date = new Date();
      date.setFullYear(year, month - 1, day);
      date.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0);
      return date;
    }
     
    export default function WorkoutForm() {
      const [_, setLocation] = useLocation();
      const { toast } = useToast();
      const queryClient = useQueryClient();
     
      const form = useForm<InsertWorkout>({
        resolver: zodResolver(insertWorkoutSchema),
        defaultValues: {
          date: formatDateToLocalISOString(new Date()),
          isRestDay: false,
          muscleGroups: [],
          notes: "",
        },
      });
     
      const mutation = useMutation({
        mutationFn: async (data: InsertWorkout) => {
          await apiRequest("POST", "/api/workouts", data);
        },
        onSuccess: () => {
          queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['/api/workouts'] });
          toast({
            title: "Success",
            description: "Workout saved successfully",
          });
          setLocation("/");
        },
        onError: (error) => {
          toast({
            title: "Error",
            description: error.message,
            variant: "destructive",
          });
        },
      });
     
      const isRestDay = form.watch("isRestDay");
     
      return (
        <div className="min-h-screen bg-background py-8">
          <div className="container max-w-2xl">
            <Card className="p-6">
              <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Log Workout</h1>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>
      );
    }
    1. client/src/components/calendar.tsx:
    TypeScript
    import { useQuery } from "@tanstack/react-query";
    import FullCalendar from "@fullcalendar/react";
    import dayGridPlugin from "@fullcalendar/daygrid";
    import type { Workout } from "@shared/schema";
    import { muscleGroupColors, restDayColors } from "@/lib/colors";
     
    export default function Calendar() {
      const { data: workouts = [] } = useQuery<Workout[]>({
        queryKey: ["/api/workouts"],
      });
     
      const events = workouts.map((workout) => {
        if (workout.isRestDay) {
          return {
            title: "Rest Day",
            date: workout.date,
            backgroundColor: restDayColors.background,
            textColor: restDayColors.text,
            borderColor: restDayColors.border,
            classNames: ['text-center'],
          };
        }
     
        // Get the first muscle group's color for the event background
        const primaryMuscleGroup = workout.muscleGroups[0];
        const backgroundColor = muscleGroupColors[primaryMuscleGroup];
     
        return {
          title: workout.muscleGroups.join(", "),
          date: workout.date,
          backgroundColor,
          textColor: '#FFFFFF',
          classNames: ['text-center'],
        };
      });
     
      return (
        <FullCalendar
          plugins={[dayGridPlugin]}
          initialView="dayGridMonth"
          events={events}
          height="auto"
          eventContent={(eventInfo) => {
            return {
              html: `<div class="text-center w-full font-medium">${eventInfo.event.title}</div>`
            };
          }}
        />
      );
    }
